法規內容.條文內容:
The term "justified reasons" depicted in the first paragraph, Article 61 of the Act includes the following conditions:
1. The water distribution pipelines are not yet roughed-in;
2. The water supply or distribution system has reached saturation point while expansion work is not yet completed;
3. Water supply encounters special problem which cannot be overcome temporarily; and
4. Other circumstances as accepted by the competent authority.
